OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCalls for windfall tax grow
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas BP's profits surge      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Oil giant BP has reported its highest  
OL,6, profit for eight years, prompting calls
OL,7, for a windfall tax on energy companies.
OL,9,FBP posted a profit of $12.8bn (#9.5bn) 
OL,10,Ffor 2021, and it made more than $4bn in
OL,11,Fthe final quarter of the year when oil 
OL,12,Fand gas prices surged.                 
OL,14,FThe jump in energy prices means        
OL,15,Fhouseholds are facing huge increases in
OL,16,Fgas and electricity bills from April.  
OL,18,FLabour said it was "only fair and      
OL,19,Fright" that energy firms making higher 
OL,20,Fprofits should pay more tax.           
